    <para id="exprate">
      For the average probability of error, the Chernoff distance is
      its exponential rate.
      <m:math display="block">
	<m:mrow>
	  <m:ci><m:msub>
	      <m:mi>P</m:mi>
	      <m:mi>e</m:mi>
	    </m:msub></m:ci>
