    <para id="relation">
      The Kullback-Leibler and Chernoff distances are related in an
      important way.  Define 
      <!--pdf-->
      <m:math>
	<m:ci><m:msub>
	    <m:mi>p</m:mi>
	    <m:mi>s</m:mi>
